Jason assembled for his crew, a number of heroes, known as the Argonauts after their ship, the Argo. The group of heroes included:: 485 
Acastus;
Admetus;
Argus, the eponymous builder of the Argo;
Atalanta;
Augeas;
the winged Boreads, Zetes & Calaïs;
the Dioscuri, Castor & Polydeuces;
Euphemus;
Heracles;
Idas;
Idmon, the seer;
Lynceus;
Meleager;
Orpheus;
Peleus;
Philoctetes;
Telamon; and
Tiphys, the helmsman
